{"tid":1393340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"噴漆使用教學","createTime":"2019-08-01T05:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T05:26:14.000Z","uid":4274,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f901888c5004e2332adefefca50e62d34eaeabad","tid":1393340,"uid":4274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:10:14.000Z","msg":"近排見多咗人做手工，所以想分享下一啲手工嘅小技巧，特別係噴漆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇試過風太大噴唔到啲遠嘢?<br />\n<br />\n覺唔覺得有時啲油唔夠集中，要噴幾浸先可以完全遮蓋透明物件?<br />\n<br />\n其實好容易解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">換噴嘴</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/29D1CHU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F29D1CHU.png&h=35f72355&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無錯就係呢種<span style=\"color: red;\">長管形噴嘴</span>(唔一定要DW40，但應該佢係最容易買到）<br />\n<br />\n呢隻管比較幼，太長可能會影響效果同埋容易堵塞，所以將佢<span style=\"color: red;\">剪成2-3cm</span>就最好啦，同埋記住要<span style=\"color: red;\">搖勻噴漆</span>，入面嘅溶劑同顏料充分咁混合先會達到最佳效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過唔使噴一次又搖一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一開始搖過就可以一直用<br />\n<br />\n萬一條管塞咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔使驚你仲有之前個噴嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n萬一噴嘴都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇有怕，直接將條管抽出嚟都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">用噴漆記得帶手套，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">必要時</span>就好揼咗佢啦</span><br />\n<br />\nSor for 1999"},{"pid":"c76e48eedd28e77e48431286fe997e46121d6c1b","tid":1393340,"uid":4274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔小心開錯台添"